==Stat Growth Formulas==

===HP Growth===

```
HP(level) = Base HP + (Level × HP Growth Rate)
HP Growth Rate = 40 HP per level (levels 1-30)
HP Growth Rate = 0 HP per level (levels 31-41, capped at 1640)
```

===MP Growth===

```
White MP(level) = Base + (Level × 2.5)
Black MP(level) = Base + (Level × 2.3)
Wizard MP(level) = Base + (Level × 2.0)
```

===Stat Growth===

```
Attack(level) = Base + (Level × 2.3)
Defense(level) = Base + (Level × 2.0)
Speed(level) = Base + (Level × 2.0)
Magic(level) = Base + (Level × 1.9)
```

All stats cap at 99.

