==Companion AI Scripting==

Companion AI uses priority-based decision trees.

===AI Decision Format===

{| class="wikitable"
! Priority !! Condition !! Action
|-
| 1 || Ally KO'd || Cast Life (if learned)
|-
| 2 || Ally HP < 30% || Cast strongest heal spell
|-
| 3 || Ally HP < 60% || Cast weaker heal spell
|-
| 4 || Enemy has weakness || Cast weakness spell
|-
| 5 || MP > 50% || Cast strongest attack spell
|-
| 6 || MP > 20% || Cast moderate attack spell
|-
| 7 || Always || Physical attack
|}

Companions never use items or run from battle.

