==Notes==

* Benjamin is the only character with variable level (1-41)
* Companions have fixed levels: Kaeli (10), Tristam (16), Phoebe (22), Reuben (28)
* HP display caps at 1640 in "Scale" mode, but internal max is 65535
* Stat calculations use Current = Base + Equipment bonuses
* Companion AI never wastes MP on already-healed targets
* All characters can equip 4 items: Weapon, Armor, Shield, Accessory

